Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.34,0:00:07.97,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Open your mind. Open your mind.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.22,0:00:24.43,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Far beyond the deep blue Earth,\nyou and I shall meet...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.43,0:00:25.80,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...as a gentle breeze goes by.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.80,0:00:29.80,AMG TITLE,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,AH! MY GODDESS
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.80,0:00:31.27,AMG TITLE,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,AH! MY GODDESS
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.27,0:00:38.41,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A snow-white feather comes fluttering\ndown, swaying gently in the air.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.41,0:00:45.52,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Without holding back, I want to\nenvelope you, my one and only love.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.52,0:00:54.93,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I know I have the power to protect\nthe one I love, right here in my hands.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.93,0:01:01.67,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Open your mind.\NJust as I've always dreamed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.67,0:01:08.58,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let the wind carry off\nyour hopes, faraway.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.58,0:01:15.35,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have wings nobody can see.\NLook, you have them, too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.35,0:01:23.66,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They'll take us to where we can be free.\NAnyone can be free.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.66,0:01:28.15,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The sky is so blue...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.73,0:02:11.17,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I didn't get a wink\nof sleep last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.21,0:02:18.18,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You can't sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.18,0:02:19.47,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.47,0:02:23.12,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,When I think that you and I\nare going to share...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.12,0:02:27.94,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...as many wonderful moments as there\nare stars in the sky, I get so excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.72,0:02:33.59,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, by the way, whenever\nwe can't sleep, we count sheep...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.59,0:02:35.16,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.16,0:02:38.90,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So you do have mysterious spells\nhere on Earth as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.90,0:02:41.94,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if you'd call it\na spell, but maybe it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.94,0:02:45.14,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All right, why don't we\ncount sheep together!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.14,0:02:47.04,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, then I'll start.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.04,0:02:48.97,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,1 sheep.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.97,0:02:51.31,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,2 sheep.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.31,0:02:53.35,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,3 sheep.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.35,0:02:55.51,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,4 sheep.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.51,0:02:57.62,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,15 sheep.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.62,0:02:59.72,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,16 sheep.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.72,0:03:02.21,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,17 sheep.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.46,0:03:05.39,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you getting sleepy yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.39,0:03:08.75,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,593 sheep!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.75,0:03:12.30,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,594 sheep.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.30,0:03:17.14,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have counted as many sheep as\nthere are stars in the sky by morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.14,0:03:18.94,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.94,0:03:21.74,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, let's keep going.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.74,0:03:25.04,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,595 sheep.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.04,0:03:28.92,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,596 sheep.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.92,0:03:32.22,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,597 sheep.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.22,0:03:35.58,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,598 sheep...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.96,0:03:40.59,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Man, to think that we're going to\nstart living together under one roof...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.59,0:03:43.26,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if I can keep up with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.26,0:03:47.43,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?\NSighing so early in the morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.27,0:03:52.57,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.57,0:03:54.54,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.14,0:03:57.68,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.68,0:04:03.94,AMG episode name,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ah! Apprenticeship, Home, and the\NGoddess{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.58,0:04:08.29,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Since there's two of us, I want to get\na place with at least two rooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.29,0:04:12.16,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But I'll have to find something\nthat costs the same as my dorm room.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.16,0:04:15.93,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to go through the hassle\nof explaining things to my folks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.93,0:04:19.57,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to come up with the\ndeficit by doing extra work...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.57,0:04:23.37,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...and I'll try to get the\nbest deal that I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.37,0:04:27.01,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to get along in this world\nwithout money.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.01,0:04:31.41,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I guess so. You can't pay rent or eat...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.41,0:04:34.95,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The fact is, without money,\nyou'll never get anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.95,0:04:36.77,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.08,0:04:39.75,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Then how about a little spell?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.75,0:04:41.08,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Spell?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.76,0:04:45.46,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Here is a wandering soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.46,0:04:50.20,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If you can hear my voice, provide\nthis soul with the Light of Life...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.20,0:04:53.86,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...with the sustenance he needs to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.50,0:04:57.67,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.67,0:04:58.49,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.97,0:05:01.00,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's that little girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.88,0:05:06.35,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I can't thank you enough\nfor helping Hijiri yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.35,0:05:10.25,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, don't mention it.\NThank you for treating us to lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.25,0:05:13.52,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hijiri, thank him properly, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.52,0:05:17.62,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Big Sister,\nare you Big Brother's wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.46,0:05:20.09,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.09,0:05:23.60,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Look, he's turning red!\NHe's turning red!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.60,0:05:26.77,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I am not his wife, but a godd...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.77,0:05:28.20,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,God?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.20,0:05:30.97,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,God, those glasses are so becoming!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.97,0:05:32.13,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.13,0:05:35.58,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You can't say things like that in public!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.58,0:05:37.74,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot say such things?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.74,0:05:40.78,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,My, how sweet that you two are so\nclose.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.78,0:05:46.05,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You know what? I've never seen anyone\nwearing such frilly, flowing clothes...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.05,0:05:47.92,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...as you before!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.92,0:05:50.19,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Are they strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.19,0:05:55.56,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Not many people dress like that in this\ncountry. Maybe you stand out a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.56,0:05:57.29,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.00,0:05:59.96,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All right, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.07,0:06:04.90,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,B-Big Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.78,0:06:15.41,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Is this better, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.25,0:06:22.88,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.43,0:06:29.86,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You can't use magic in public like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.86,0:06:31.33,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.33,0:06:35.33,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I can only use that kind of power\nseveral times a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.33,0:06:38.34,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If people find out that\nyou have special powers...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.34,0:06:40.87,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...there's going to be a huge uproar.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.87,0:06:45.65,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And if that happens, we might not\nbe able to stay together anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.65,0:06:47.98,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If that should come to pass...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.98,0:06:51.98,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...the System Force will take effect,\nand there could be chaos.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.98,0:06:56.91,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Right, so I guess you're going to have\nto learn all about living in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.91,0:06:59.46,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, apparently so.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.46,0:07:02.40,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let's try and make this work somehow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.40,0:07:03.56,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.56,0:07:07.57,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,First of all, we've got to find\na new place to live. Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.57,0:07:08.70,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.34,0:07:13.67,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, we're looking for a\nplace for the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.67,0:07:17.08,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of place do you have in\nmind?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.08,0:07:21.48,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A place with a kitchen and two rooms\nwith its own bath and toilet if possible...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.48,0:07:26.91,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...and a parking spot for my motorcycle\nfor 15,000 yen a month or less!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.15,0:07:33.09,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I know I'm asking for the impossible,\nbut I thought I'd ask you to try anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.66,0:07:36.92,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We do not have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.63,0:08:09.96,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, man...\NReality is as tough as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.96,0:08:15.13,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A lot of hardship goes into leading\none's life here on Earth, I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.13,0:08:18.54,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but everyone\ngoes through hardship.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.54,0:08:21.61,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's why people work hard everyday.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.61,0:08:23.51,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Work hard, did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.51,0:08:28.84,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If you're doing what you love, working\nhard won't seem like such an effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.84,0:08:32.89,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Take me, for instance. If it's to fulfill my\ndream of building my own bike...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.89,0:08:34.95,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...I can work hard for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.95,0:08:38.71,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I find that very appealing, Keiichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.71,0:08:43.15,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But the reality is that\neverything takes money!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.15,0:08:47.46,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Right now this is my entire fortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.46,0:08:51.90,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So we have to find a place to live with\nthe help of that ''money'', is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.90,0:08:53.01,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.01,0:08:59.38,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Then let me ask the Holy Spirit if there\nis a place for the two of us to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.38,0:09:02.22,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Can you do something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.22,0:09:07.48,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We are two wandering souls...\ntwo souls who seek a safe abode.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.72,0:09:12.46,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,O Spirit of the 2,000-Yen Bill,\nbearing all the hopes of this man...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.46,0:09:17.06,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Reveal to us now the path\nyou would have us take!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.17,0:09:24.97,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, crap! My entire fortune!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.97,0:09:26.14,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go after it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.14,0:09:27.10,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All right!{\i0}\NLet's go after it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.38,0:09:44.16,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't find it, having no place to live\nwill just be the start of our problems!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.16,0:09:45.79,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.79,0:09:48.03,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.03,0:09:50.36,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,My 2,000-yen bill!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.36,0:09:53.03,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tariki Hongan Temple{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.14,0:10:02.61,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.25,0:10:12.24,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, I came this close to\nlosing my entire fortune!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.24,0:10:16.11,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Still, I never knew\nthere was a temple here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.09,0:10:24.50,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There are no evil spirits here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.50,0:10:27.10,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's quite a lovely place!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.10,0:10:30.63,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, I'd better take back my...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.67,0:10:35.64,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.61,0:10:38.30,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.88,0:10:44.14,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi!\NKeiichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.14,0:10:49.58,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,M-My entire fortune...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.58,0:11:14.81,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.81,0:11:19.19,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Last I remember, I got totally clobbered\nover the head by somebody...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.19,0:11:22.68,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to be fine, Keiichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.39,0:11:28.36,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.36,0:11:33.83,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The whole time I was sleeping,\nmy head was on Belldandy's lap?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.40,0:11:37.60,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Are you still in pain?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.60,0:11:40.61,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, I'm okay now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.61,0:11:43.61,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So you woke up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.61,0:11:45.58,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oshou!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.98,0:11:49.95,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm terribly sorry for what I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.95,0:11:53.45,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I mistook you for a thief\ngoing after the offerings.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.45,0:11:57.72,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Even given my habit of jumping to\nconclusions, it was a serious mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.72,0:12:03.16,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, I should apologize. What I did\nwas totally misleading! I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.16,0:12:06.33,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give it another thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.33,0:12:08.03,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.03,0:12:10.27,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,As for this...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.27,0:12:14.97,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let me return this money to you.\NThat's the least I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.04,0:12:22.25,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, could you let us pay for a night's\nlodging here with that money?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.25,0:12:25.95,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have a place to live,\nand we have nowhere to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.95,0:12:30.06,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If 2,000 yen isn't enough, I'll do\nwhatever I can to make it up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.06,0:12:31.85,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.10,0:12:48.97,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That money is your payment for helping\nme take care of this temple today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.97,0:12:53.47,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Your food and lodging for tonight\nwill be provided separately.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.71,0:12:58.72,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to enjoy working here.\NGet yourselves ready at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.72,0:13:00.99,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir! Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.54,0:13:19.77,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you get every\nlast inch of the floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.77,0:13:22.63,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Use your back muscles, already!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.31,0:13:28.11,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that simple!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.85,0:13:35.91,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.32,0:13:37.91,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.59,0:13:41.59,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You need to follow the girl's example!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.59,0:13:42.66,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.14,0:13:55.44,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.71,0:13:58.21,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All right, take another lap!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.21,0:14:00.94,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.45,0:14:06.05,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The image of Buddha is any\ntemple's greatest treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.05,0:14:08.95,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,When you've poured\nyour entire heart into...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.95,0:14:12.45,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...its polishing, then it is\na true apprenticeship.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.53,0:14:18.10,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I can see everything begin to\ngleam as I polish, more and more.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.10,0:14:21.53,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's just like\nI'm cleansing my own soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.04,0:14:30.47,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But what's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.48,0:14:35.05,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What is the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.05,0:14:38.51,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, uh... it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.53,0:14:56.99,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That Oshou is one violent guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.99,0:15:00.57,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure he means no harm by it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.57,0:15:04.18,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How are we gonna get\nthis temple tidied up?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.18,0:15:09.00,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The lawn's overgrown with weeds. It'll\nbe a major hassle pulling them out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.48,0:15:12.89,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But if we do it together,\nwe'll have fun with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.89,0:15:16.12,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, let's just hope we have fun...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.26,0:15:22.09,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.40,0:15:26.43,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Belldandy...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.43,0:15:30.64,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I call forth to thee in the name\nof the autumn leaves. Heed my voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.64,0:15:33.40,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Deliver that man into safety!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.35,0:15:42.78,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.49,0:15:49.96,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Was that you... just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.96,0:15:54.69,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, but I've broken my promise to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.69,0:15:57.16,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I used magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.16,0:15:59.80,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But you didn't have a\nchoice this time, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.80,0:16:04.77,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, you saved me even though\nit meant breaking your promise...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.77,0:16:07.17,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...that makes me happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.17,0:16:10.04,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Belldandy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.31,0:16:12.47,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.65,0:16:18.22,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look, we better\nfix that roof right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.22,0:16:20.04,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose so!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.49,0:16:22.86,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That skill of hers...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.86,0:16:24.68,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.68,0:16:27.42,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Who in the world is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.73,0:16:40.19,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I was sure she'd show her true self\nat night if she were a specter...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.61,0:16:47.74,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,However, I can't let my guard down.\nI've got to keep watch all night.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.59,0:16:59.22,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.84,0:17:18.24,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Reveal yourself, Holy Bell!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.25,0:17:27.15,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, let us sing together!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.99,0:17:33.02,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Restore this desolate land\nto its former glory!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.03,0:17:39.50,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What! Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.17,0:17:42.83,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Blunder!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.97,0:17:50.00,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Where on earth is\nthis voice coming from?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.00,0:18:14.56,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Holy Bell!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.84,0:18:28.48,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't measure up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.48,0:18:32.65,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That guardian angel, that beautiful voice\nthat could capture anyone's heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.65,0:18:37.46,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Everything she does transcends the\nlevel of enlightenment I have attained.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.46,0:18:41.56,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I still have a long, long way to go...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.01,0:18:59.01,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This time I got a good night's sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.01,0:19:00.88,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Keiichi!{\i0}\NThis time I got a good night's sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.88,0:19:02.71,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Oshou!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.71,0:19:04.00,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.42,0:19:12.95,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,My Tariki Hongan Temple,\nI bid you farewell for a short time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.99,0:19:15.59,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oshou!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.59,0:19:18.36,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.76,0:19:21.77,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I still have a lot of\ntraining ahead of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.77,0:19:26.27,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I must go on a nationwide pilgrimage\nso that I can reach full enlightenment!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.27,0:19:28.57,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please send me off with a smile!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.57,0:19:30.44,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But why, all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.44,0:19:33.51,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I was made painfully aware\nof my own inexperience.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.51,0:19:35.65,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I must aspire to be like Belldandy...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.65,0:19:39.85,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...to one day have the ability to\nsend others to heaven by singing in...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.85,0:19:43.32,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...a glorious voice along\nwith a guardian angel!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.32,0:19:44.66,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Guardian angel?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.66,0:19:48.09,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Until that time, I am leaving\nthis temple in your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.09,0:19:49.86,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Farewell!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.36,0:19:54.20,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What did he mean by guardian angel?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.20,0:19:56.77,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I think he must be referring to this...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.77,0:19:58.77,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.77,0:20:00.84,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Her name is Holy Bell.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.84,0:20:04.94,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,She protects me, and is always\nwith me. She's my higher self.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.81,0:20:11.08,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So it was the Oshou jumping\nto conclusions again, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.08,0:20:15.85,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Still, thanks to the Oshou's kindness,\nwe now have a place to live, don't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.85,0:20:18.71,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I should fix that hole in the roof...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.71,0:20:22.89,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But isn't that one more thing\nto look forward to, Keiichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.86,0:20:51.91,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Morisato Ya{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.26,0:20:59.10,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we'll have to\nborrow the Oshou's stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.10,0:21:01.90,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...until I bring over the stuff\nI left at the dorm.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.90,0:21:02.83,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.83,0:21:06.54,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting paid tomorrow, so that'll take\ncare of whatever else we need, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.54,0:21:08.77,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...we shouldn't waste money.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.77,0:21:10.88,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.88,0:21:15.11,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, I think I've put you\nthrough a lot of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.11,0:21:19.65,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no. Since we're going through\nit together, I'm enjoying it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.15,0:21:22.42,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.89,0:21:25.65,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.73,0:21:28.32,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Look...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.66,0:21:32.66,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You know, if we had pretty cups\nlike these to drink our tea out of...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.66,0:21:35.53,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...it would taste delicious, wouldn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.53,0:21:37.77,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You like tea, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.77,0:21:38.80,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.01,0:21:47.91,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.12,0:21:51.98,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.98,0:21:56.62,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A moment ago you said we shouldn't\nwaste money, but you just did anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.62,0:22:00.36,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's just my way of thanking\nyou for saving me yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.36,0:22:06.19,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But isn't it strange? We went shopping,\nyet we still have money left over.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.03,0:22:12.37,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, since we have more money,\nwe should've bought some tea, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.37,0:22:14.57,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And a tea service, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.57,0:22:18.44,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,When we do, I'll make\ndelicious tea everyday!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.44,0:22:20.68,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That'll be great!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.03,0:22:39.73,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}One day when I woke up...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.43,0:22:51.14,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A day like any other...\nanother one just beginning.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.14,0:23:00.62,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There you are, yawning...\nyour face is still so sleepy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.62,0:23:07.29,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because each peaceful day\nwe share is a miracle to me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.29,0:23:13.90,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is where my heart\nwill always return...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.90,0:23:16.76,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Forever...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.76,0:23:22.67,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's only one thing I wish for.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.67,0:23:29.11,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I chase after the same dream,\nwherever it may go.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.11,0:23:35.12,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The love I feel for you\ngives me strength.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.12,0:23:41.36,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}May tomorrow be as joyful as today...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.36,0:23:45.89,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's my wish...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.31,0:24:00.78,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The Queen, one who reigns at the\nhighest level of the universe...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.78,0:24:03.32,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...leading the way with\nher beauty and power.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.32,0:24:05.95,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The sparks are sure to fly\nwhen these two meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.95,0:24:08.52,AMG next episode name,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode:\NAh! The Queen and the Goddess!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.52,0:24:12.28,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really have to come to blows\nover this ''Campus Queen'' title?
